
Test-driven Development (TDD)
  - Write the smallest test case
  - Run the test
  - think why it failed
  - write code to pass the test
  - refactor the codes

  Behavior-Driven Development (BDD)
   - test = specifications of system behavior

  RSpec
    - Testing Library
    - for Ruby
    - for in-production app

    Setup Code
      mkdir spec

      gem "rspec"
      bundle install --path .bundle

